Class HeartModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chute.sdk.v2.model.HeartModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class HeartModel
extends Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    The HeartModel class represents a concept of asset heart. Each heart consists of: links, date of creation and update, identifier, asset ID and album ID the flag belongs to.
